timeline.bodyText:
I'm wondering if it would be better to have another method to be used when configuration.roles() is empty.
Also, the subject mask can be computed in the same loop above. Example:
  for (Principal principal : principals) {
     Set<String> roleNames = roleMapper.principalToRoles(principal);
     if (roleNames != null) {
        for (String role : roleNames) {
           Role globalRole;
           if (allRoles.add(role) && (globalRole = globalRoles.get(role)) != null) {
              subjectMask |= globalRole.getMask();
           }
        }
     }
  }

